'''周期性調整市盈率'''（{{lang-en|Cyclically adjusted price-to-earnings ratio}}，簡稱CAPE、Shiller P/E或P/E 10 ratio）<ref name="tel-isa">{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/personalfinance/investing/isas/10931281/New-Isas-are-here-but-is-it-the-worst-time-to-buy-as-FTSE-100-nears-record-high.html|title=Super Isas are here - is it the worst time to buy?|work=The Telegraph|date=28 Jun 2014|accessdate=4 July 2014|author=Evans, Richard|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202031030/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/personalfinance/investing/isas/10931281/New-Isas-are-here-but-is-it-the-worst-time-to-buy-as-FTSE-100-nears-record-high.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="investopedia">{{Cite web|title=P/E 10 Ratio|url=http://www.investopedia.com/terms/p/pe10ratio.asp|accessdate=4 July 2014|work=Investopedia|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214081720/http://www.investopedia.com/terms/p/pe10ratio.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>是指一家公司去除[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]因素的實際股價除以10年間該公司去除通貨膨脹因素的[[每股收益|每股收益]]的平均值。<ref name="vector">{{Cite web|title=Price to 10 Year Inflation Adjusted Earnings|url=http://www.vectorgrader.com/indicators/cyclically-adjusted-price-earnings|accessdate=4 July 2014|work=VectorGrader.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713005433/http://www.vectorgrader.com/indicators/cyclically-adjusted-price-earnings|archivedate=2014-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>這一概念主要用于评估未來10到20年时间内投資一家公司的股票可能帶來的回报。周期性調整市盈率是由美国经济学家[[羅拔·席勒|羅拔·席勒]]於1998年提出<ref>{{Cite web|title=A 股市场特征研究（六）——从周期调整市盈率（CAPE）看中美股市当前的估值水平|url=https://www.htsec.com/jfimg/colimg/upload/20180301/23771519889968452.pdf|accessdate=|author=海通證券|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719115250/https://www.htsec.com/jfimg/colimg/upload/20180301/23771519889968452.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Morningstar: 淺談以周期性調整市盈率作預測|url=https://www2.hkej.com/wm/article/id/1212496|accessdate=|author=信報|